msgstr ""

msgctxt "LookPicture_01"
msgid "That's amazing!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
msgctxt "Talk_00"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Hrm...<2.pa> What was written on \n"
"this stone monument?"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid "<1.so>The shrine's beautiful today, too!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (long)
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Oh, it's you! The shrine's glowing\n"
"today, too!\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>You aren't just a normal lad, are you?<3.pa>\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>I'm just happy that the mystery was \n"
"solved!<5.pa> I don't want to do more \n"
"snooping than is absolutely necessary!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (long)
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Whoa! <2.pa>I don't know what was closer to\n"
"bowling me over, the surprise or the\n"
"way the ground was shaking! <3.pa>Haha!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: pause (longer)
#. 4: text_size
#. 5: text_size
msgctxt "Talk_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>So the two who needed to \"find their\n"
"place\" were you and me...<2.pa> Makes sense.\n"
"\n"
"Good job figuring that one out!<3.pa>\n"
"<4.te_si>I sure never would have...<5.te_si>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: raw
#. 4: sound
#. 5: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Huh? <2.pa>You're fixing to go explore\n"
"that shrine?<3.ra><4.so>Oh, sorry. <5.pa>I won't keep you any longer.\n"
"Off you go!"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: pause (short)
msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There really does seem to be something\n"
"special about you, though...\n"
"\n"
"<2.so>But I'm just happy that the riddle is\n"
"solved!<3.pa> You're a clever, mystery-solving\n"
"guy, and that's all I need to know!"
msgstr ""

